    "formula": "active = (flags & ACTIVE) || (flags & TRAILED); ALIGN_DISABLED: txform = xform; ALIGN_BILLBOARD: axis=normalize(sort_direction), rotated=Rodrigues(axis, custom[channel]); new_up=rotated*align_up; local=mat3(normalize(cross(new_up, sort_direction)), new_up, sort_direction)*mat3(txform); then txform[3].xyz += velocity*frame_remainder. inactive: txform basis=0, translation column=(-inf,-inf,-inf,0). write (3D, transposed): instances[i*5+0..2]=transpose(txform) rows 0..2; [i*5+3]=color; [i*5+4]=custom; column-major mat algebra, every operation rounded to binary32",
